<p class="MsoNormal">This year, an elite
group of athletes will act as National Sport Day Ambassadors, displaying the
advantages of sports and inspiring local community to be a part of the great
event. Among those athletes, Olympic shooters, Bahia Al Mansour, Aya Magdi and
Qatar former football star, Mansour Muftah.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">In a press release
after being selected as the NSD ambassador, shooter Aya Magdi said “The
National Sport Day represents a golden chance and new step to break the routine
life through sport by meeting all friends and family members in a festive sport
scene”.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">NSD ambassador,
Mansour Muftah said “Sports have changed my life and enabled me to learn the
best human values, I belief that the NSD will inspire the nation (men, women,
youth and kids) to gain physical fitness and create the new generation of
starts for Qatar sport movement”.</p><p class="MsoNormal">EVENT SCHEDULE: <a href="http://www.sportday.qa/events">http://www.sportday.qa/events</a></p>